### Phase 2 â€“ Controlled Launch

* Retail + SME segments
* Support & card journeys
* Call center integration

### Phase 3 â€“ Advanced Experiences

* Proactive alerts
* Personalized insights
* AI-assisted recommendations (non-selling first)

